<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 16:08:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>比利时禁止以色列定居者在西岸实施反巴勒斯坦暴力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/belgium-bans-israeli-settlers-committing-anti-palestinian-violence-in-the-west-bank/0000018c-44b1-df9c-a5ff-f7bb7abd0000</link><description>比利时总理效仿了拜登最近的制裁措施，并表示将推动欧盟效仿。他警告称，自 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击以来，西岸定居者的暴力行为已达到历史最高水平，“针对平民的暴力行为将会产生后果”</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 15:57:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/belgium-bans-israeli-settlers-committing-anti-palestinian-violence-in-the-west-bank/0000018c-44b1-df9c-a5ff-f7bb7abd0000</guid></item><item><title>“好犹太人”与“坏犹太人”：为什么支持巴勒斯坦的抗议活动有问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/good-jew-vs-bad-jew-why-pro-palestine-protests-have-a-problem/0000018c-43d1-db23-ad9f-6bd936010000</link><description>我一直抗议以色列的占领和系统性的反阿拉伯歧视，但我不会加入纽约的亲巴勒斯坦抗议活动。我永远不会接受有毒测试，要求我谴责其他犹太人，也不会与任何将杀害以色列人视为“抵抗”合法化的人一起游行</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 15:41:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/good-jew-vs-bad-jew-why-pro-palestine-protests-have-a-problem/0000018c-43d1-db23-ad9f-6bd936010000</guid></item><item><title>来自耶路撒冷的信：战时我的家人、我的国家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/letter-from-jerusalem-my-family-my-country-at-wartime/0000018c-4394-db23-ad9f-6bdc67490000</link><description>10 月 7 日，我们从露营之旅中醒来，听到爆炸声。战争的恐怖开始显现：不仅是哈马斯的火箭弹，而且我们意识到我们的表弟也是从以色列被绑架到加沙的人之一。他什么时候回家？</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 15:35:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/letter-from-jerusalem-my-family-my-country-at-wartime/0000018c-4394-db23-ad9f-6bdc67490000</guid></item><item><title>犹太人和常春藤盟校之间的美好友谊结束了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/the-beautiful-friendship-between-jews-and-the-ivy-league-is-over/0000018c-44cd-db23-ad9f-6cdd58760000</link><description>加沙战争加剧了这一趋势，但它早在几年前就开始了：常春藤盟校背弃了犹太人。现在犹太校友正在回报我们</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 15:16:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/the-beautiful-friendship-between-jews-and-the-ivy-league-is-over/0000018c-44cd-db23-ad9f-6cdd58760000</guid></item><item><title>以色列外交部长为内塔尼亚胡之子亚伊尔和党员下令发​​放外交护照</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-foreign-minister-orders-diplomatic-passports-for-netanyahus-party-members-son/0000018c-4472-db23-ad9f-6cfadeee0000</link><description>外交部专业工作人员认为发放护照不合适，但外交部长伊莱·科恩绕过了他们。一位熟悉外交部门的消息人士表示，“这味道特别难闻”</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 15:06:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-foreign-minister-orders-diplomatic-passports-for-netanyahus-party-members-son/0000018c-4472-db23-ad9f-6cfadeee0000</guid></item><item><title>被释放的以色列人质的漫长康复之路才刚刚开始</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/the-long-road-to-recovery-for-freed-israeli-hostages-has-only-just-begun/0000018c-3f62-d6a5-afae-bf72c4b20000</link><description>以色列从未面临过如此规模的重建项目。很难预测人质的完全康复之路将如何结束，甚至是否结束</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 15:04:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/the-long-road-to-recovery-for-freed-israeli-hostages-has-only-just-begun/0000018c-3f62-d6a5-afae-bf72c4b20000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡，无视美国关于加沙的想法，后果自负</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-ignore-the-u-s-ideas-about-gaza-at-your-peril/0000018c-43f0-d2d5-abef-f7f72feb0000</link><description>在华盛顿，人们认识到以色列与哈马斯的战争不符合或源于任何政治目标。因此，两个月后，美国人单方面提出了自己的框架，尽管他们知道极端主义的内塔尼亚胡政府永远不会同意。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 14:04:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-ignore-the-u-s-ideas-about-gaza-at-your-peril/0000018c-43f0-d2d5-abef-f7f72feb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵宣称加沙北部建筑是查巴德之家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-proclaim-a-chabad-house-in-northern-gaza-damaged-building/0000018c-43a1-db23-ad9f-6bf9bd320000</link><description>这个想法似乎来自一些在特拉维夫学习的美国犹太学院学生，他们计划在南下时张贴更多标志。查巴德运动的已故领导人坚信以色列必须保留对以色列所有圣经土地的控制权</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 13:02:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-proclaim-a-chabad-house-in-northern-gaza-damaged-building/0000018c-43a1-db23-ad9f-6bf9bd320000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵记录在西岸射杀巴勒斯坦残疾人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-documented-shooting-a-palestinian-with-special-needs-in-west-bank/0000018c-4411-d2d5-abef-f5771f430000</link><description>34 岁的塔里克·阿布·阿贝德 (Tariq Abu &amp;#39;Abed) 在希伯伦下班回家时，士兵拦住了他，要求他出示身份证件。没有它，他们就用枪指着他。当他做出解释的手势时，他们开枪打死了他。他的母亲与《国土报》分享了他的账户</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 12:15:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-documented-shooting-a-palestinian-with-special-needs-in-west-bank/0000018c-4411-d2d5-abef-f5771f430000</guid></item><item><title>“试图点燃其他战线：”以色列反对派领导人炮轰极右翼圣殿山/阿克萨清真寺游行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/jewish-activists-to-rally-in-jerusalems-old-city-for-full-control-over-temple-mount/0000018c-4414-d89c-a3ef-4e3762e30000</link><description>此次游行仅限 200 人参加，预计沿着耶路撒冷老城穆斯林区的路线进行，并呼吁犹太人对该大院进行“完全控制”</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 12:02:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/jewish-activists-to-rally-in-jerusalems-old-city-for-full-control-over-temple-mount/0000018c-4414-d89c-a3ef-4e3762e30000</guid></item><item><title>由于几乎没有互联网接入和令人困惑的以色列国防军推文，加沙人不知道该去哪里</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/with-hardly-any-internet-access-and-confusing-idf-tweets-gazans-dont-know-where-to-go/0000018c-3e7b-d53d-a7fc-beff3f3e0000</link><description>以色列国防军的阿拉伯语发言人发布了一张难以理解的地图，上面有乱码的地名，加沙人将用它来做出生死攸关的决定；人权组织报告称，地图上的避难所已经因人潮拥挤和必需品缺乏而崩溃</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 11:20:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/with-hardly-any-internet-access-and-confusing-idf-tweets-gazans-dont-know-where-to-go/0000018c-3e7b-d53d-a7fc-beff3f3e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长下令不经审判就拘留被指控袭击巴勒斯坦人的定居者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-defense-minister-orders-settler-accused-of-palestinians-assault-held-without-trial/0000018c-3f85-d2e7-ab8d-bff518cb0000</link><description>随着美国打击针对约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人的暴力行为的压力越来越大，约阿夫·加兰特签署了针对塔尔·伊农·达尔迪克的命令。极右翼部长本-格维尔暗示国防部长“很困惑，忘记了朋友和敌人的区别”</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 11:04:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-defense-minister-orders-settler-accused-of-palestinians-assault-held-without-trial/0000018c-3f85-d2e7-ab8d-bff518cb0000</guid></item><item><title>工党领袖梅拉夫·米凯利宣布退出政坛，称以色列面临“严重危机”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/labor-party-head-michaeli-announces-shes-leaving-politics-cites-israels-grave-crisis/0000018c-43b0-d89c-a3ef-4fb31afb0000</link><description>米凯利在去年的选举中坚持认为她的政党应与梅雷茨分开竞选，这对以色列左翼构成了打击，而梅雷茨未能跨过选举门槛。她表示，新的领导力竞赛将在四个月后举行，希望“战争届时能够结束”</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 10:42:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/labor-party-head-michaeli-announces-shes-leaving-politics-cites-israels-grave-crisis/0000018c-43b0-d89c-a3ef-4fb31afb0000</guid></item><item><title>数十名哈马斯战士在加沙向以色列军队投降；黎巴嫩向以色列发射反坦克导弹造成平民死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article-live/under-u-s-pressure-israeli-cabinet-approves-more-fuel-for-gaza/0000018c-4281-db23-ad9f-6ad9e0600000</link><description>以色列国防军继续在加沙地带北部和南部推进地面行动 ■ 以色列国防军公布了周三在加沙战斗中丧生的三名士兵的名字 ■ 《纽约时报》报道，美国司法部正在调查 10 月 7 日哈马斯谋杀 30 多名美国公民的事件 ■ 欧盟外交博雷尔部长和世卫组织总干事表示支持联合国秘书长古特雷斯援引第99条。 ■ 自10月7日以来，以色列至少有1,200名平民和士兵被杀；加沙仍有超过 138 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙至少有 15,899 人死亡</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 04:46:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article-live/under-u-s-pressure-israeli-cabinet-approves-more-fuel-for-gaza/0000018c-4281-db23-ad9f-6ad9e0600000</guid></item><item><title>拜登热衷于让以色列在加沙对哈马斯发动攻势，但设定了明确的价格</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/biden-is-allowing-israels-gaza-offensive-to-proceed-but-with-a-price/0000018c-40f3-d245-a38c-cbf3afc70000</link><description>美国对以色列行动的支持似乎取决于提供人道主义援助 ■ 人质家属警告说，随着以色列国防军将攻势扩大到加沙地带南部，战斗正冒着他们亲人的生命危险</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 04:28:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/biden-is-allowing-israels-gaza-offensive-to-proceed-but-with-a-price/0000018c-40f3-d245-a38c-cbf3afc70000</guid></item><item><title>不要指望很快就会建立以色列-黎巴嫩缓冲区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-lebanon-buffer-zone-not-anytime-soon/0000018c-40f2-d868-addd-d0f26ed00000</link><description>随着以色列推动真主党与其北部边境保持距离，黎巴嫩在目前的政治体制下几乎无法在任何问题上做出决定，更不用说保护边界等重大事务了</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 04:27:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-lebanon-buffer-zone-not-anytime-soon/0000018c-40f2-d868-addd-d0f26ed00000</guid></item><item><title>犹太大屠杀纪念馆对大学校长“借口”对犹太人进行种族灭绝的呼吁感到“震惊”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/yad-vashem-appalled-by-university-presidents-excusing-calls-for-genocide-against-jews/0000018c-4154-d868-addd-d1f454750000</link><description>大屠杀纪念活动主席将美国精英大学校长的证词描述为“对历史的基本无知”</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 00:01:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/yad-vashem-appalled-by-university-presidents-excusing-calls-for-genocide-against-jews/0000018c-4154-d868-addd-d1f454750000</guid></item><item><title>大学校长回避有关种族灭绝犹太人呼吁的问题后，白宫感到愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/white-house-outraged-as-college-presidents-skirt-questions-on-calls-for-genocide-of-jews/0000018c-40f5-db23-ad9f-68fde0de0000</link><description>众议院共和党人从一开始的意图就是公开嘲笑大学校长。即使考虑到这种背景，总统们还是成功地平息了美国犹太社区的疏远和激怒。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 21:50:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/white-house-outraged-as-college-presidents-skirt-questions-on-calls-for-genocide-of-jews/0000018c-40f5-db23-ad9f-68fde0de0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最新预算首次投票通过，部长们批评非战争开支</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/israels-updated-budget-passes-in-first-vote-as-ministers-criticize-non-war-expenses/0000018c-40d0-d868-addd-d0f00b960000</link><description>在没有利库德集团部长尼尔·巴尔卡特和约夫·加兰特以及部长本尼·甘茨的支持的情况下，以色列议会在所需的三轮投票中的第一轮就通过了预算的更新版本</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 21:43:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/israels-updated-budget-passes-in-first-vote-as-ministers-criticize-non-war-expenses/0000018c-40d0-d868-addd-d0f00b960000</guid></item><item><title>这就是生与死：武装以色列平民是一项可怕的安全政策</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/thats-life-and-death-arming-israeli-civilians-is-a-terrible-security-policy/0000018c-40a5-db23-ad9f-68fd78bd0000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日袭击事件以来，以色列已收到超过 25 万份新枪支许可证申请，这一数字超过了过去 20 年的总和。数据表明，这不会让国家变得更安全——相反</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 20:33:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/thats-life-and-death-arming-israeli-civilians-is-a-terrible-security-policy/0000018c-40a5-db23-ad9f-68fd78bd0000</guid></item></channel></rss>